OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FShowers
OL,6,For some longer outbreaks of rain on
OL,7,FFriday and Saturday, the rain perhaps
OL,8,Fheavy and thundery at times. Early
OL,9,Frain clearing to showers on Sunday.
OL,10,FBreezy at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
